text: Lauren Jane Sieprath (born 23 October 1989) is a New Zealand water polo player. She is a member of the New Zealand national team. She played at the 2009 World Aquatics Championships and 2011 World Aquatics Championships. She played for California State University, Long Beach's women's water polo team. == References == Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand water polo players
